item.title: Apply
item.description: Apply below for available units at Sumerset Apartments: When applying to rent at Sumerset Apartments please be prepared to provide: Social Security Card Driver’s License or other Government Photo ID Proof of Employment and your 2 most recent Paystubs Non-refundable Applicant fee via Money Order A separate application is required for each potential resident over the age of 17
